description:
Console App for SpecSync for Azure DevOps (for .NET Framework v4.*). For systems with .NET Core v3 installed, we recommend to install SpecSync.AzureDevOps as a .NET Core tool. 
      SpecSync for Azure DevOps is a synchronization tool that synchronizes Gherkin feature files with Azure DevOps (TFS/VSTS).
summary: Console App for SpecSync for Azure DevOps (for .NET Framework v4.*). For systems with .NET Core v3 installed, we recommend to install SpecSync.AzureDevOps as a .NET Core tool.
title: Console App for SpecSync for Azure DevOps (for .NET Framework v4.*)
